1. Introduction
1.1 Overview

Merchanta AI is an AI-powered ecommerce intelligence platform that helps merchants understand how AI systems like ChatGPT, Gemini, Perplexity, and AI shopping agents perceive, rank, and recommend their products.

The platform combines:

Shopify ingestion pipelines
AI semantic analysis
Conversational shopping simulation
Vector retrieval systems
Recommendation readiness scoring
AI-generated optimization insights
